    body
        #page
            .section#home
                .row: .col-md-6.col-md-offset-6
                    .mast
                        h1 Castaway Labs
                        p A development team dedicated to bringing together your vision and ideas into reality
                            | fusing the cutting edge design trends and technology.
                        nav(role='navigation')#nav-sup
                            ul.nav
                                li: a(href='#about') about
                                li: a(href='#team') team
                                //-li: a(href='#portfolio') portfolio
                                //-li: a(href='#testimonials') testimonials
                                li: a(href='#contact') contact
            .section#about
                .row.section-headline
                    h1.section-title about
                    p.lead Castaway Labs &reg; provides professional and efficient web and mobile solutions to fit your business needs. Our team will work with you in one-on-one meetings to fine tune your product to your liking.
                .row.section-content
                    .col-md-4
                        .thumbnail-about: i.fa.fa-lightbulb-o
                        h2.thumb-title Idea
                        p Your idea deserves the very best hands working on it. We are dedicated to
                            | bringing your vision to life to produce the digital solution your business
                            | needs.
                    .col-md-4
                        .thumbnail-about: i.fa.fa-pencil
                        h2.thumb-title Design
                        p Our designers will create the very best UI for your users. We will work in
                            | close collaboration with you to translate your design requirements and wish
                            | list into your digital solution.
                    .col-md-4
                        .thumbnail-about: i.fa.fa-code
                        h2.thumb-title Development
                        p Our team utilizes open source projects, as well as content management systems to
                            | provide your business with the solution that best fits your needs.
            .section#team
                .row.section-headline
                    h1.section-title team
                    p.lead Meet our team of professional problem-solvers, handpicked for their talent and dedication, from around the world.
                .row.section-content
                    .col-md-2.col-md-offset-1
                        .thumbnail: img(src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f0842c23c56c3b4445bedd05f6489583.jpg?s=120')
                        h4 Alan Campbell
                        p Team Manager
                    .col-md-2
                        .thumbnail: img(src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/7e2e31912fa0b07ff61861a0f98d691c.jpg?s=120')
                        h4 Matej Kramny
                        p Developer
                    .col-md-2
                        .thumbnail: img(src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/5297b18750aa6994c5d45f673a2dc758.jpg?s=120')
                        h4 Anže Jenšterle
                        p Developer
                    .col-md-2
                        .thumbnail: img(src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/360b5e1a549813e102042b97113096b7.jpg?s=120')
                        h4 Mark Hendriks
                        p Developer
                    .col-md-2
                        .thumbnail: img(src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e40af4e9f7ed6cef5236445b7f7b3fc7.jpg?s=120')
                        h4 Zia Ur Rehman
                        p Developer
